Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,太好啦 抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那么大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,举杯庆祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那么请在这里填写联络方式与姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,退场时间为明天早上10点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,柴火可以随意在林中拾取并使用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:20:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一二三四 二二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,今天在打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 其实我独自出来露营了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,凛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,现在刚到露营场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.41,0:22:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪座露营场？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那是秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不然给彼此发露营场的照片 来猜猜看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.24,0:22:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里
